The '''''Era of Rebellion Sourcebook''''' was to be an RPG sourcebook, written by [[Pablo Hidalgo]] for [[West End Games]] and set to cover events of the [[Star Wars (1977)|''Star Wars'' (1977)]] comics. It was canceled, although Hidalgo reused much of it for his ''[[The Starhoppers of Aduba-3]]'' article in [[Star Wars Gamer 4|''Star Wars Gamer'' 4]].

